snippet.title: Hyper DBZ 4.2B Released + Free Download
snippet.description:
TeamZ2 is proud to present this sweet intermediate update to our build of Hyper Dragon Ball Z, version 4.2B! List of changes inside the video + when you boot the build for the first time. Bring the list back afterwards by pressing F1.

http://justnopoint.com/HyperDBZChamp.rar - USA link
http://xgargoyle.mugenguild.com/HyperDBZChamp.rar - EUR link
Size: 641 MB.
Separate characters can be downloaded here: http://network.mugenguild.com/balthazar/chars_z2.html

Team Z2 Facebook:     https://www.facebook.com/HyperDBZ/
Team Z2 Twitter:     https://twitter.com/z2_team
Hyper DBZ Discord:     https://discordapp.com/invite/JJHbNGe
Mugen Fighters Guild: http://mugenguild.com/forum/hyper-dbz.412
Patreon:      https://www.patreon.com/TheBalthazar
